com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.validator.resolution
Interface IDeployResolutionGenerator

All Known Implementing Classes:
DeployActionGenerator, DeployParameterizedResolutionGenerator, DeployResolutionGenerator
public interface IDeployResolutionGenerator

Interface implemented by a generator for SOA deploy status resolutions.

Not intended to be directly implemented. Extend DeployResolutionGenerator.

Generators are declared using the DeployCorePlugin.PLUGIN_ID. ICommonDeployExtensionConstants.TAG_RESOLUTION_GENERATOR extension point.
